{"tid":1446634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟還擊有無得諗","createTime":"2019-08-11T15:10:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T21:50:23.000Z","uid":193549,"like":37,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"2040d0c78e06091dbfdbb44d789932a6b5361d26","tid":1446634,"uid":193549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:10:05.000Z","msg":"太古個到真係......<br />\n<br />\n啲狗衝埋黎個陣唔好退 後面個個捉住最前排個個唔好俾佢被人捉走 如果班狗扑佢地就後面啲人打翻佢地 一齊退 個情況就會變成兩班人推撞 而唔係單個俾人捉住打 跟住越捉越多<br />\n好似佢地啲防線咁後面捉實最前面個個 一個捉實一個 唔好被人捉走<br />\n<br />\n唔好一味退 又唔還擊 起碼都叫算試過 <br />\n<br />\n還掂預左犧牲 就唔好淨係退 試下推住或者捉住啲狗"},{"pid":"76d97f2582a783a2eaed52d37cf989cca500b45e","tid":1446634,"uid":193549,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:10:57.000Z","msg":"純討論 純粹想知得唔得"},{"pid":"3d4022734ae1124171d61419ed3915cbcc87cf6d","tid":1446634,"uid":235754,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:11:12.000Z","msg":"其實一定要還擊 只係無人敢做個個出頭鳥"},{"pid":"f74197cef419ee01133cd5cce18268696662553e","tid":1446634,"uid":108337,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:11:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日全面封鐵封路 有狗打狗</span></span>"},{"pid":"2c04c0ca8e212881532ce6576a21740bcb3eba2e","tid":1446634,"uid":193549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:11:38.000Z","msg":"好想知得唔得"},{"pid":"ef79a9dfa6c58ceff173ea645cbde67339793c96","tid":1446634,"uid":193549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:11:59.000Z","msg":"多啲人入黎討論得唔得！！！！"},{"pid":"adad6d68af3a522bf527f15dafc126749584a5bf","tid":1446634,"uid":280305,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:12:06.000Z","msg":"而家至識咁諗？<br />\n人多唔識團結根本冇用！<br />\n見親都係一有人被捉！<br />\n所有人走晒！<br />\n次次都係咁！"},{"pid":"f6a4723b1f915fc22fa355c72998f3ad512cb391","tid":1446634,"uid":268775,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:12:29.000Z","msg":"總之所有暴力打狗的行為都係班黑警